sources.title: The Unknown 1927 colorized
sources.description: From IMDB: A criminal on the run hides in a circus and seeks to possess the daughter of the ringmaster at any cost.https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0018528 Very spooky early horror by Tod Browning, starring Lon Chaney and Joan Crawford. Became Public Domain as of January 1 2023 as was the case with all 1927 movies. Colorized using DeOldify and Avidemux's Old Photo filter. Music track made by me, from free Public Domain classical music files at Midiworld.com and mfiles.co.uk. (Note: Although this movie is public domain, the colorization is copyright by me. My colorized movies are freely uploaded for free personal use. Please don't put them on your own YouTube channel and monetize them. Thanks.)
